rComments: Best prof ever. Must listen and attend lectures.  Interesting things to say, don't agree with othe comment he's willing and open to other views.  Take his class.
Very approachable.very hot.very funny. love going to his classes. he loves to teach. must attend all classes to get a good mark. by far one of my favourite profs.

This is a good prof., he makes the subject very interesting.  He is witty, but make no mistake he is difficult in marking, not just hard marker, but difficult.  I did not get a good mark in his course, but will take any course he teaches, because he is very apporachable.  He knows his stuff well.

Mahdi was an awesome prof, so approachable and always willing to share humourous anecdotes!  Even though it was his first year teaching the course, he managed just fine. I greatly recommend any of his courses.
I concur, this is an amazing professor! knows his stuff, easy to talk to, very friendly, and yes, very good looking. recommend taking anything he teaches, he makes the course very interesting.
An amazing prof and very good looking. Makes the course very easy and fun to attend.
